        "timestamp": "2019-11-15 00:57:54.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nSorry to cause confusion, in my haste I missed a key qualifying phrase.  Should have written: .. the first person **IN ONAP** to use these global-jjb templates ..",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
